        <ThingDef ParentName="BaseWeapon_BladelinkGnollstrom">
        <defName>MeleeWeapon_GnollstromScythe</defName>
        <label>Gnollstrom Reaper</label>
            <description>Clearly designed by a fan of a certain space ninja video game and good weaponsmithery, this blade has proliferated out into the Gnollstrom organization as an extremely effective though highly expensive melee weapon. They are hard to find, they cost a lot of money, and if someone comes at you with one, kill them before they get close.</description>
        <statBases>
          <MarketValue>50000</MarketValue>
          <Mass>2</Mass>
        </statBases>
        <equippedAngleOffset>-35</equippedAngleOffset>
        <graphicData>
          <graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
          <texPath>Things/Item/Equipment/WeaponMelee/ReaperPrimeGnollstrom</texPath>
          <color>(200,200,255)</color>
        </graphicData>
        <soundInteract>Interact_BladelinkMonoSword</soundInteract>
        <meleeHitSound>MeleeHit_BladelinkMonoSword</meleeHitSound>
        <smeltable>false</smeltable>
        <weaponClasses>
          <li>Melee</li>
          <li>MeleePiercer</li>
        </weaponClasses>
        <tools>
          <li>
            <label>handle blade</label>
            <capacities>
              <li>Cut</li>
            </capacities>
            <power>28</power>
            <cooldownTime>1.1</cooldownTime>
          </li>
          <li>
            <label>points</label>
            <capacities>
              <li>Stab</li>
            </capacities>
            <power>39</power>
            <cooldownTime>1.1</cooldownTime>
            <armorPenetration>0.7</armorPenetration>
          </li>
          <li>
            <label>edges</label>
            <capacities>
              <li>Cut</li>
            </capacities>
            <power>35</power>
            <cooldownTime>1.1</cooldownTime>
            <armorPenetration>0.9</armorPenetration>
          </li>
        </tools>
    </ThingDef>

    <ThingDef ParentName="BaseWeapon_BladelinkGnollstrom">
        <defName>MeleeWeapon_GnollstromLionsword</defName>
        <label>Gnollstrom Halberd</label>
            <description>A lion sword that's been hacked to emit a laser. High damage slow to wield. \nThis weapon has an onboard persona roughly hacked into it, that can bond to only a single person. The wielder and intelligent weapon can synchronize their reflexes and attack with frightening speed, accuracy, and creativity. Once bonded to a wielder, the weapon's persona will refuse to be wielded by anyone else.</description>
        <statBases>
          <MarketValue>5000</MarketValue>
          <Mass>2</Mass>
        </statBases>
        <equippedAngleOffset>-65</equippedAngleOffset>
